import React, { Component, useState, useEffect } from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Navbar from "./components/navbar";
import Home from './pages/inicio'
import Birds from './pages/pajaros'
import Acount from './pages/cuenta/login'
import Register from './components/login-register/register_component'

const App = () => {
  const [login, setLogin] = useState(false)
  return (
    <Router>
      <Navbar />
      <Switch>
        <Route path='/' exact component={Home} />
        <Route path='/pajaros' exact component={Birds} />
        {
          login
            ?
            <Route path='/acceder' exact component={Acount} />
            :
            <Route path='/acceder' exact component={Acount} />
        }
        <Route path='/registrarse' exact component={Birds} />
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
